(83, 'how to fix vscode bracket when autocompleting statement in Python ?', 'how-to-fix-vscode-bracket-when-autocompleting-statement-in-python', 'In this tutorial we are going to fix vscode bracket issue when autocompleting statement in Python .', '<p>Vscode is an very Powerfull and famous Code Editor for Developers. Developers using it for all language. It have very Powerfull feature for developers like inbuilt Terminal, Auto Suggestion feature, tons of extension for increasing productiviy.</p>\r\n<p>But sometime auto suggestion stoped working .Sometime It simple lag from the hardware of the System. But sometime it is not due to hardware </p>\r\n<h2>What is the problem ?</h2>\r\n<p>people experiences that when writing any tag in python eg.  print in python .</p>\r\n<p>It completing print when We  press p but not adding parenthesis() with it.  The simple reason is some setting mistake.  </p>\r\n<p>In this tutorial we are going to solve this issue if you have one above then you may read it. </p>\r\n<h2>Solution to vscode auto  brackets issue</h2>\r\n<ol>\r\n    <li>first open Visual Studio Code </li>\r\n    <li>Click on gear option at left-bottom side</li>\r\n    <li>Now choose Settings from options\r\n    </li><p>open settig.json file by clicking</p><img src=\"https://qnastop.com/upload/83/vscode error autocomplete.png\" alt=\"vscode python auto bracket error\" class=\"imga\">\r\n    <li><p>See my settings below</p><img src=\" https://qnastop.com/upload/83/vscode error autocomplete1.png\" alt=\"vscode python auto bracket error\" class=\"imga\"></li>\r\n    <li>Copy and paste below line to your file like displayed above <p>\"\"python.analysis.completeFunctionParens\": true\"</p></li>\r\n\r\n</ol>\r\n<p style = \"background-color:black; color:white;\">{\r\n    \"editor.autoClosingBrackets\": \"always\",\r\n    \"editor.autoClosingQuotes\": \"always\",\r\n    \"files.autoSave\": \"afterDelay\",\r\n    \"workbench.editorAssociations\": {\r\n        \"*.ipynb\": \"jupyte